<document>
  <properties>
    <title>Release Notes</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="RSS Release Notes">
      <subsection name="1.04.00">
        <ul>
          <li>Upgrade to run on Hippo CMS 7.5.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.03.00">
        <ul>
          <li>Upgrade to run on Hippo CMS 7.4.</li>
          <li>Translations for field names in English and Dutch.</li>
          <li>Includes updater module to upgrade from 1.02.04, 05 and 06.
            Before that, the namespace version is different so a self-implemented upgrader with a namespace visitor is to be used.</li>
          <li>Changed the Maven groupId of the artifacts from org.onehippo.addon to org.onehippo.forge.feed</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.06">
        <ul>
          <li>In HST query, use a limit to avoid performance penalty. The limit
            is the same as the item count in the configuration document.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.05">
        <ul>
          <li>Upgrade to run on Hippo CMS 7.3</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.04">
        <ul>
          <li>Bump rss namespace to http://www.hippoecm.org/hst/nt/rss/1.3</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.02">
        <ul>
          <li>New component to support rss feed on hippo facet beans</li>
          <li>Bump rss namespace to http://www.hippoecm.org/hst/nt/rss/1.2</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.01">
        <ul>
          <li>Bump rss namespace to http://www.hippoecm.org/hst/nt/rss/1.1</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.02.00 and below">
        <ul>
          <li>RSS namespace is http://www.hippoecm.org/hst/nt/rss/1.0</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>
